short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows a rank trend line and projected rank on osu! user profiles.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension adds the following improvements to user profiles on the osu! website:

- Displays a trend line to the ranking graph
- States a projected ranking above the ranking graph calculated using the trend line
